          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"scoped-css\">Scoped CSS</h2>\n<div class=\"language-js codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\">// \ud83c\udf18 CSS Scope Inline (https://github.com/gnat/css-scope-inline)</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">window</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">cssScopeCount</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">??=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mf\">1</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">window</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">cssScope</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">??=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"ow\">new</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">MutationObserver</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nx\">mutations</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nb\">document</span><span class=\"o\">?</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">body</span><span class=\"o\">?</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">querySelectorAll</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;style:not([ready])&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"nx\">forEach</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nx\">node</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"kd\">var</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">scope</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;me__&#39;</span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">window</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">cssScopeCount</span><span class=\"o\">++</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"nx\">node</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">parentNode</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">classList</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">add</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nx\">scope</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"nx\">node</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">textContent</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">node</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">textContent</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">replace</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"sr\">/(?:^|\\.|(\\s|[^a-zA-Z0-9\\-\\_]))(me|this|self)(?![a-zA-Z])/g</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;$1.&#39;</span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"nx\">scope</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">replace</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"sr\">/((@keyframes|animation:|animation-name:)[^{};]*)\\.me__/g</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;$1me__&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"nx\">node</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">setAttribute</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;ready&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">})</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}).</span><span class=\"nx\">observe</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">document</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">documentElement</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"nx\">childList</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kc\">true</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">subtree</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kc\">true</span><span class=\"p\">})</span>\n</code></pre></div></span>"
